Foursquare Gospel Church, Saabo District Headquarters, will hold its annual District Convocation from Saturday July 16, 2022. The event which will begin with couples dinner, will feature business delegates meetings, while the grand celebration will be on Sunday July 24, 2022. The programme was christened, ‘Power to Soar’, adopted from Isaiah 40:31, even as the hosts, the District Overseer, Rev and Rev (Mrs.) Albert Aina, assured the public of divine elevation and enlargement beyond expectations. Other anointed ministers expected at the church include Pastor & Mrs. Bisi Adewale, Prophet Peter Adeniyi Olowoporoku and guest artiste, Kakaaki Jesu, among others.